# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [2.2.0] - 2022-04-27
### Added
 - DUMSES-Hybrid is now released with an autotools configure script

### Changed

### Deprecated
 - Makefiles examples located in makefiles/ are now deprecated

### Removed

### Fixed
 - indentation of preprocessing directives in src/modules/solvers/solver.f90
 - declaration of nccl and cudafor in src/subroutines/parallel.f90
 - declaration of ciso in src/modules/commons.f90 with OpenACC
